	   <tr><td colspan=2>Let's ignore the numbers for a second and talk logic.<br><br>Locustlure - at level 45+ this is not a good weapon. Slow proc = sure way to be plastered against the nearest wall. I mean that unless your tank has some solid aggro (or he's an SK, hehe) the combination of the slow effect on the weapon and the massive damage output will probably net you quite a bit of aggro.<br><br>Bloodpoint - decent ratio, though the proc might cause some small problems, as noted above. Not as big a deal though<br><br>Intricate Silver Rapier - best ratio of the bunch, but it's a tad slow for a rogue weapon.<br><br>I'd say go for dual Bloodpoints just because the taunt isn't that great on the lifetap proc.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
